      "time_str": "01:12.470",
      "text": "就算痛苦流泪都也无所谓",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 77.38,
      "time_str": "01:17.380",
      "text": "我也不会在乎谁错谁对",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
